\"\"%F(%\"bGF(F(*(\"#5F()F&\"\"$F()F,\"\"#F(F(*(F.F()F&F2F()F,F0F(F(*(
F'F(F&F()F,F+F(F(*$)F,F'F(F(" }}{PARA 11 "" 1 "" {XPPMATH 20 "6(\"\"&
\"#5F$\"\"\"F%F#" }}}{EXCHG {PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 0 "" }{TEXT 297 
32 "For the rest we will run a loop." }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 0 "" 
}}}{EXCHG {PARA 0 "> " 0 "" {MPLTEXT 1 0 41 "for n from 6 to 10\ndo\ne
xpand((a+b)^n)\nod;" }}{PARA 11 "" 1 "" {XPPMATH 20 "6#,0*$)%\"aG\"\"'
\"\"\"F(*(F'F()F&\"\"&F(%\"bGF(F(*(\"#:F()F&\"\"%F()F,\"\"#F(F(*(\"#?F
